    <title>容器编排</title>
    <link href="/2021/02/03/%E5%AE%B9%E5%99%A8%E7%BC%96%E6%8E%92/"/>
    <url>/2021/02/03/%E5%AE%B9%E5%99%A8%E7%BC%96%E6%8E%92/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="uwsgi-flask-nginx-docker-compose-进入容器编排（本地）"><a href="#uwsgi-flask-nginx-docker-compose-进入容器编排（本地）" class="headerlink" title="uwsgi + flask + nginx docker_compose 进入容器编排（本地）"></a>uwsgi + flask + nginx docker_compose 进入容器编排（本地）</h2><h3 id="1-创建docker-compose-yml-文件"><a href="#1-创建docker-compose-yml-文件" class="headerlink" title="1. 创建docker_compose.yml 文件"></a>1. 创建docker_compose.yml 文件</h3><figure class="highlight dts"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs dts"><span class="hljs-symbol">version:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;2&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">services:</span> <br><span class="hljs-symbol">  webapp1:</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">    build:</span> ./drex_api<br><span class="hljs-symbol">    container_name:</span> drex_api<br><span class="hljs-symbol">    ports:</span><br>      - <span class="hljs-string">&quot;8000:8000&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">    volumes:</span><br>      - /Users<span class="hljs-meta-keyword">/linliuan/</span>docker_info:/mnt<br><span class="hljs-symbol">  nginx:</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">    image:</span> nginx<br><span class="hljs-symbol">    volumes:</span><br>      - ./nginx.conf:<span class="hljs-meta-keyword">/etc/</span>nginx/conf.d/default.conf<br><span class="hljs-symbol">    depends_on:</span><br>      - webapp1<br><span class="hljs-symbol">    ports:</span><br>      - <span class="hljs-string">&quot;8887:80&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-创建nginx-conf-文件"><a href="#2-创建nginx-conf-文件" class="headerlink" title="2. 创建nginx.conf 文件"></a>2. 创建nginx.conf 文件</h3><figure class="highlight nginx"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs nginx"><span class="hljs-section">server</span> &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-attribute">listen</span> <span class="hljs-number">80</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-attribute">server_name</span> <span class="hljs-number">0.0.0.0</span>; <br>    <span class="hljs-attribute">location</span> / &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-attribute">include</span> uwsgi_params;<br>        <span class="hljs-attribute">uwsgi_pass</span> webapp1:<span class="hljs-number">8000</span>;<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-创建uwsgi的ini文件"><a href="#3-创建uwsgi的ini文件" class="headerlink" title="3. 创建uwsgi的ini文件"></a>3. 创建uwsgi的ini文件</h3><figure class="highlight ini"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ini"><span class="hljs-section">[uwsgi]</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">master</span> = <span class="hljs-literal">true</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">callable</span>=app<br><span class="hljs-attr">socket</span> = :<span class="hljs-number">8000</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">chdir</span> = /drex_api<br><span class="hljs-attr">module</span> = app<br><span class="hljs-attr">processes</span> = <span class="hljs-number">2</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">enable-threads</span> = <span class="hljs-literal">true</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">logto</span> = /drex_api/app.log<br><span class="hljs-attr">post-buffering</span> = <span class="hljs-number">8192</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">smart-attach-daemon</span> = /tmp/celery_drex.pid celery -A celery_server.celery_app worker --pidfile=/tmp/celery_drex.pid<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="4-创建Dockerfile-文件"><a href="#4-创建Dockerfile-文件" class="headerlink" title="4. 创建Dockerfile 文件"></a>4. 创建Dockerfile 文件</h3><figure class="highlight dockerfile"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs dockerfile"><span class="hljs-comment"># 所采用的基础镜像</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">FROM</span> python:<span class="hljs-number">3.7</span>.<span class="hljs-number">0</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 为镜像添加标签</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">LABEL</span><span class="bash"> version=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;v1&quot;</span> description=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;Docker deploy Flask&quot;</span> by=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;Dalao&quot;</span></span><br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">RUN</span><span class="bash"> mkdir /drex_api</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 配置工作目录</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># WORKDIR /usr/src/app</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">WORKDIR</span><span class="bash"> /drex_api</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 将主机中目录内容拷贝到镜像目录下</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># COPY . .</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">COPY</span><span class="bash"> . /drex_api</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># EXPOSE 8000</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 在镜像容器中执行命令</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">RUN</span><span class="bash"> pip install -r requirements.txt</span><br><br><br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 容器启动时执行指令,每个Dockerfile只能有一条CMD命令</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># CMD [&quot;uwsgi&quot;, &quot;--ini&quot;, &quot;/drex_api/uwsgi_docker.ini&quot;]</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">CMD</span><span class="bash"> [<span class="hljs-string">&quot;uwsgi&quot;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;--ini&quot;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;/drex_api/uwsgi_docker_compose.ini&quot;</span>]</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>文件目录大致是这样的情况</p><p><img src="/2021/02/03/%E5%AE%B9%E5%99%A8%E7%BC%96%E6%8E%92/16123293531773.jpg"></p><h3 id="5-docker-compose-命令执行"><a href="#5-docker-compose-命令执行" class="headerlink" title="5. docker-compose 命令执行"></a>5. docker-compose 命令执行</h3><p>执行命令</p><figure class="highlight ebnf"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ebnf"><span class="hljs-attribute">docker-compose up -d</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>创建docker的images,并且同时创建 container 并启动。</p><p>启动后<code>docker ps</code> 显示container </p><p><img src="/2021/02/03/%E5%AE%B9%E5%99%A8%E7%BC%96%E6%8E%92/16123299192478.jpg"></p><h3 id="6-编排中遇到的问题"><a href="#6-编排中遇到的问题" class="headerlink" title="6. 编排中遇到的问题"></a>6. 编排中遇到的问题</h3><blockquote><ol><li>docker 中运行的容器服务不可以使用后台启动， docker 发现不了后台启动的服务, 现象会是刚启动docker 服务后立马停止。</li><li>docker 内容器的通信需要创建的时候注意下： 这里uwsgi的配置文件中socket = :8000 是只可以容器间的端口可见。socket ==&gt; http 的时候，容器间就不可见，但外部就可以进行直接的访问。</li><li>uwsgi 中的属性 daemonize 是指将 uwsgi 后台运行。如果指定了这个配置项目后，现象就如1中所示。</li></ol></blockquote>]]></content>
    
    
    
